  "notes": "Somali in official Latin orthography (1972). C = pharyngeal /ʕ/; X = pharyngeal /ħ/; DH = retroflex /ɖ/; Q = uvular /q/; KH = velar fricative /x/. Vowel length is phonemic (doubled letters). Tone is high/low marked only in formal contexts. The language has two noun genders and grammatical tone.",
